                     <interp inst="t18320705-147-person1270" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I took the prisoner, and have the handkerchief; there were two other handkerchiefs on the prisoner.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I saw this handkerchief on the pavement; I turned down Bread-street, and was coming back again, when the prosecutor took me - I told him I had found it.</p>
